  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluation of the dipping status of blood pressure (wether blood pressure decreases at night)
      and renal functional reserve and wether non-dippers (those whose blood pressure does not
      decrease at night) can be modulated to dippers with potassium treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
